      "title": "Activist Piyath Nikeshala remanded",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Colombo Fort Magistrate\u2019s Court has ordered to place activist Piyath Nikeshala in remand custody until August 26.",
        "He was charged in connection with forcibly entering the Prime Minister\u2019s Office on July 14 and was produced before the court today."
      ],
